# API Endpoints

LocalCA provides a comprehensive API for certificate management operations.

## Backend API Endpoints

- `/api/ca/info` - Get CA information
- `/api/certificates` - List all certificates
- `/api/certificates/:id` - Get certificate details
- `/api/certificates/create` - Create a new certificate
- `/api/certificates/renew/:id` - Renew a certificate
- `/api/certificates/revoke/:id` - Revoke a certificate
- `/api/certificates/delete/:id` - Delete a certificate
- `/api/settings` - Get/update application settings

## Frontend API Routes

- [app/api/ca-info/](mdc:app/api/ca-info) - CA information endpoints
- [app/api/certificates/](mdc:app/api/certificates) - Certificate management endpoints
- [app/api/delete/](mdc:app/api/delete) - Certificate deletion endpoint
- [app/api/renew/](mdc:app/api/renew) - Certificate renewal endpoint
- [app/api/revoke/](mdc:app/api/revoke) - Certificate revocation endpoint

## ACME Endpoints

- `/.well-known/acme-challenge/:token` - HTTP-01 challenge validation
- `/acme/directory` - ACME directory endpoint
- `/acme/new-nonce` - Get new nonce
- `/acme/new-account` - Create new account
- `/acme/new-order` - Create new certificate order
- `/acme/finalize-order/:id` - Finalize certificate order
- `/acme/certificate/:id` - Download certificate

